Privacy Policy

Last updated: [Nov 1,2024 ]

MyTailor is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information, particularly as it pertains to the limited data required for essential app functionalities.

1. Information We Collect
MyTailor is designed to limit the collection and use of user data. The app only collects the following information to facilitate basic functionalities:

Account Information: During registration (sign-up) and login, we collect:

Email Address
Password (stored securely using industry-standard encryption methods)
Password Reset: In the event of a password reset, users may be required to provide an email address to verify their identity and reset their password.

MyTailor does not collect or use any additional personal data beyond what is required for these purposes.

2. How We Use Your Information
The limited data collected is used solely to provide and enhance core app functions:

Account Creation and Authentication: To allow users to register, log in, and access their accounts securely.
Password Recovery: To facilitate a secure password reset process if a user forgets their password.
3. Data Security
We take the security of your data seriously. All sensitive information, such as passwords, is encrypted and stored securely. We follow industry best practices to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of your personal information.

4. Sharing Your Information
MyTailor does not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties. User data is not shared externally, and we do not display any personal information publicly.

5. Display of Images
MyTailor includes images of clothing items. These images are solely for visual representation purposes and do not involve or collect any user data.

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy
MyTailor may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or for operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We encourage you to review this policy from time to time.

